{
  "title": "Dark Gooey Spanish Octopus Pulpo A La Gallega",
  "description": "A vegetarian friendly Spanish dish featuring beer and kombu cold extract, this pulpo a la gallega is a midnight craving must have, with a rich mustardy flavor and gooey texture.",
  "cuisine": "Spanish",
  "diet": [
    "vegetarian"
